00:00:22,042 --> 00:00:26,585
history was as a designer for Insomniac Games and more recently my work with Heart Machine

7
00:00:26,846 --> 00:00:28,026
on the game Hyper Light Drifter.

8
00:00:28,931 --> 00:00:33,437
Today I'm going to talk about the transition I made from working on large AAA 3D action

9
00:00:33,477 --> 00:00:38,965
shooters such as Resistance 3 and Sunset Overdrive to Hyper Light Drifter which is a 2D overhead

10
00:00:39,245 --> 00:00:43,731
action game and what level design processes and principles carried over between 3D and

11
00:00:43,751 --> 00:00:43,771
2D.

