00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:53,502
So everything I talk about will be through that lens.

15
00:00:54,502 --> 00:00:58,927
Also I'm going to be showing several full‑sized maps from Hyper Light Drifter which will reveal

16
00:00:58,967 --> 00:00:59,668
secret areas.

