245
00:13:46,006 --> 00:13:50,808
It gives you a good vantage point of how to approach the combat and it's just a very safe

246
00:13:50,848 --> 00:13:54,170
feeling compared to that's where the danger is, here's where the safety is.

247
00:13:54,650 --> 00:13:59,212
And then of course once the combat starts, it's no longer safe to stay up there and player

248
00:13:59,232 --> 00:14:00,973
