00:16:27,431 --> 00:16:30,393
a level to achieve like a level‑wide sense of pacing.

291
00:16:31,333 --> 00:16:35,515
It can also mean just like physically enclosing a combat area from surrounding areas.

292
00:16:36,495 --> 00:16:41,037
It can also mean isolating in terms of time, so things like controlling waves, spawning

