00:17:19,557 --> 00:17:22,059
And there's a couple of these throughout the game,

307
00:17:22,580 --> 00:17:24,641
but you can sort of spot them when you go through.

308
00:17:24,701 --> 00:17:27,504
They just feel a little more encapsulated

309
00:17:27,584 --> 00:17:28,585
from the immediate space.

