332
00:18:47,843 --> 00:18:52,885
That meant you had to fight with no access to any refuge space, and it ended up being

333
00:18:52,905 --> 00:18:58,187
a really good tool for adding tense punctuation moments to combat without needing to vary

334
00:18:58,267 --> 00:19:00,268
enemy composition or anything like that too much.

